{"tid":368724,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一齊分享下細個好撚驚既經歷","createTime":"2017-08-21T18:01:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-22T10:18:45.000Z","uid":1627,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1b72857d3402061b61eb81a43cf4fbe6d7991ca3","tid":368724,"uid":1627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T18:01:18.000Z","msg":"小一嗰陣自己攞住錢去左屋企樓下文具鋪買左個20蚊既老翻搖搖，俾完錢之後發覺唔係咁鍾意紅色，就自己去出面偷偷地換左個差唔多包裝但藍色既搖搖，返到屋企一睇先知原來係百幾蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嗰陣真係好撚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嚇到之後幾個月行過間文具鋪都要勁快咁走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 後尾搬左屋就冇左件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f617ea58c228c927203a358c02b549e8f785501","tid":368724,"uid":51978,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T18:06:11.000Z","msg":"報左警 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13ac7e325aab9b2d3f75e89de7e017ba8b791c97","tid":368724,"uid":1627,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T18:07:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>報左警 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你係咪個老闆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係既話講聲對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e2f6297e0739c7307aa43e2ba39d63573f142c6","tid":368724,"uid":137997,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T18:24: